+------------+
|   README   |
+------------+

To build the code, type:   make

To build the ctags, type:  ./make-ctags

To execute the code, type: ./compile <code_file>

Note: 'code' is a demo test file in this directory


Assumptions list :
----------------

1. 'global' keyword is valid only for 
   <program_body> -> <declaration> , not for 
   <procedure_body> -> <declaration>

2. A local variable name is unique inside a 
   procedure, but can be re-used across 
   different procedures

